  "prompt": "Where can I get the solutions of resonance sheets and dpps?",
  "response": "You can typically find solutions for resonance sheets and DPPs (Daily Practice Problems) on several platforms. Here are some suggestions:\n\n1. **Official Website**: Check the official website or platform where the resonance materials are provided. Often, they have a dedicated section for solutions or additional resources.\n\n2. **Coaching Classes**: If you are enrolled in a coaching institute, they might provide access to solutions for various study materials and practice papers.\n\n3. **Online Forums**: Websites like Stack Exchange, Quora, or Reddit may have community members who can share or discuss solutions.\n\n4. **Social Media Groups**: Look for groups on platforms like Facebook or Telegram where students share resources related to competitive exams.\n\n5. **YouTube**: Many educators and students post solution walkthroughs for various study materials, including resonance sheets and DPPs.\n\n6. **Study Groups**: Forming or joining a study group can help you get access to shared resources and solutions.\n\nAlways make sure to use solutions responsibly and focus on understanding the concepts rather than just copying answers.",
